data.description: This flat 9.54 acres is ready for your dream plans. Sitting just off Vaughn Road and only 15 minutes from the airport this is the convenient location you have been looking for. This land is flat and ready for your hobby farm, massive garden, horses, etc. This property also comes with a "bonus" 1,367 Square foot home built in 2015 (not eligible for any mortgage, would make a great storage building). There is no water or septic currently on the land however, water and electricity are at the street. The land sits outside of city limits, which means there may be fewer restrictions on what you can do with the property. However, it's worth noting that certain uses, such as mobile homes or multi-family housing, would require a permit/permission from the county. Come see this gorgeous parcel of land and then make it your own! All improvements on the land sold as-is.
